<dt class='comment-author blog-author blogger-comment-icon' id='c758231593693951400'>
<a name='c758231593693951400'></a>
<a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/01778305776209193697' rel='nofollow'>Jess</a>
said...
</dt>
<dd class='comment-body' id='Blog1_cmt-758231593693951400'>
<p>
Hi, Lisa<br />Well, I can't promise that it will be exactly the same as a Cleveland cassata, but it is certainly "in the spirit of."  I'm proud to say that this cake has gotten rave reviews around here, so hopefully it will do the trick for you, too.  Happy baking! (And happy birthday, if that's what you'll be celebrating with this cake.)  By the way, if you would like to try this cake with a lemony twist, take a look over <A HREF="http://www.sweetamandine.com/2009/05/all-at-once.html" REL="nofollow">here</A>.
</p>
