OK, more from me on this, my first layer cake! <br /><br />Did you trim the layer&#39;s edges to make them even? I did, since there was some mushrooming puffiness on the top of the cakes. I threw them in a bowl with some strawberries and custard for a quick cook&#39;s trifle (to munch while preparing the cake).
</p>
